            "notes": "There's a speed check done before allowing the scope.\r\n\r\n    80 == crouch, 128 == walk, 256 == run\r\n\r\nLimit is currently set at 127. So while crouching, you are about 30% slower than walking.\r\nNot sure about this, as I feel it would change the gameplay (ie, taking cover easily while sniping).",
